snippet.title: Taiko no Tatsujin: Rhythm Festival — Announcement Trailer - Arriving on New Platforms!
snippet.description:
◤#TaikonoTatsujin: Rhythm Festival 
Will be available on PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S, Windows PC and STEAM® on November 7!✨◢

For the first time in home-release, the game supports 120 FPS! Look forward to new platform-exclusive collaborative songs and mini characters.🎵

Click here for the official website! https://bnent.eu/TNTRhythmFestival
